locations.name: 기원
locations.notes: Located in Euljiro (힙지로), a trendy area that was once an industrial district. The name '기원' has a double meaning, referring to its history as a go (바둑) playing establishment 30 years ago and the concept of origin. Operated by Kang Woong, a jazz record producer and musician. Serves natural wines (80% of wine list) and features lo-fi audio pairing with jazz music. Plays modern jazz on vinyl during weekdays. Features live jazz performances every Saturday. Reservations for performances are taken via Instagram DM. Performance schedules are announced one week in advance on Instagram; visitors can get a one-month schedule by visiting the venue directly. Shares a floor with '화담' (@hwadam_winebar), a wine tteokbokki restaurant.

address_text.en: 304ho, 14, Samil-daero 12-gil, Jung District, Seoul, South Korea

notes.ko: 을지로(힙지로)에 위치한 곳으로, 한때 공업 지구였던 트렌디한 지역입니다. '기원'이라는 이름은 30년 전 바둑을 두는 곳이었다는 역사와 기원의 개념을 이중적으로 의미합니다. 재즈 음반 프로듀서이자 음악가인 강웅이 운영합니다. 내추럴 와인(와인 리스트의 80%)을 제공하며, 로파이 오디오와 재즈 음악을 페어링합니다. 주중에는 바이닐로 모던 재즈를 틀고, 매주 토요일에는 라이브 재즈 공연이 있습니다. 공연 예약은 인스타그램 DM을 통해 받습니다. 공연 일정은 인스타그램에 일주일 전에 공지되며, 방문객은 직접 방문하여 한 달 일정을 알 수 있습니다. 와인 떡볶이 레스토랑인 '화담'(@hwadam_winebar)과 같은 층을 공유합니다.
notes.en: Located in Euljiro (힙지로), a trendy area that was once an industrial district. The name '기원' has a double meaning, referring to its history as a go (바둑) playing establishment 30 years ago and the concept of origin. Operated by Kang Woong, a jazz record producer and musician. Serves natural wines (80% of wine list) and features lo-fi audio pairing with jazz music. Plays modern jazz on vinyl during weekdays. Features live jazz performances every Saturday. Reservations for performances are taken via Instagram DM. Performance schedules are announced one week in advance on Instagram; visitors can get a one-month schedule by visiting the venue directly. Shares a floor with '화담' (@hwadam_winebar), a wine tteokbokki restaurant.
